<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">When you are lvl 50, you get 10 points of mana per 1 point of int/wis...after 50, it's a little bit higher...if you are 20+, i would say go with the int till you get 200, then try to get some mana items...if you are under 20, get some mana items(ie: blackened sapphire stuff is really good at low lvls...hp and mana buff) until you are high enough where the extra int makes a difference<hr>Suinadie Gogglefizzer<br>
52nd lvl Gnomish Heretic<p>

Master Brewer<br>
